### expected behavior
upload single or many files from the web interface. 

### actual behaviour
upload hangs, ram and cpu are pegged

### steps to reproduce
1. restart apache to force quit execution
2. login
3. attempt to upload single or many files again

### server configuration
operating system: windows xp and windows 8

web server: xampp, apache

database: mysql 5.5.27

php version: 5.4.7

owncloud version: 5

### client configuration
browser: chrome 19.0.1084.56

operating system: windows xp sp3, windows 8

